Wait!

Using staging for development is no longer allowed, unless you have a valid reason. To develop in NR1 you must use dev, which uses data from staging and can be accessed at https://dev-one.newrelic.com/.
Staging UI is being considered by UXP a production environment given that it is used to monitor our own systems in production. As such, we ask you to use dev instead, where all platform UI PRs are canaried before going to staging, and where extra debugging capabilites are provided. You can read more about it in a LumApps post we published.

Local nerdpacks failed to load

You requested to load local nerdpacks for development through a query parameter, however we could not find a local server working on your machine.
Make sure you have got it working by running nr1 nerdpack:serve on your nerdpack, then reload the page. For further information, please proceed to the Development Center.
